                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6131" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1546</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8824 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">百度收购YY直播：直播时代百度的突围之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Baidu acquires YY live :Baidu&#39;s &quot;Breakthrough&quot; in the era of live broadcasting</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鞠晓伟，张龄唯</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">百度在线网络技术（北京）有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">百度；YY直播；并购理论；互联网收购</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Baidu; YY Live;M &amp; A Theory;Internet Acquisition</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">摘要：进入新市场是每一个企业在本领域做到天花板或是当现有领域的生存空间受到严重挤压时都会做出的战略选择。尽管各个企业进入新市场的初始目的不同，但是最终目的都是为了获利和获得更加长远的发展。由于并购动因理论、并购风险理论和并购整合理论的长足发展，使得企业并购理论和实践的发展非常迅速，成为管理学最活跃的领域之一。本案例通过该理论对百度收购YY直播的过程进行复盘，以百度为主体，聚焦并购、战略管理等理论知识。通过本案例，来探索当下互联网行业之间如何进行资源匹配来实现自身效益、如何进行收购、如何应对在收购中出现突发问题以及如何在移动端盛行的当下，通过多元化战略寻找新的营收增长点、打造新型移动产业生态。希望通过本案例的介绍，可以帮助学生对于现有网络生态、数字经济、企业并购、战略选择等有了更加深入的了解。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Abstract：Entering a new market is a strategic choice that every enterprise achieves the ceiling in the field or makes when the living space in the existing field is severely squeezed. Although the initial purpose of enterprises entering the new market is different, the ultimate goal is to profit and gain more long - term development. Due to the rapid development of merger and acquisition motivation theory, merger risk theory and merger integration theory, enterprise merger theory and practice develop very rapidly, and has become one of the most active fields of management. This case reviews the process of Baidu&#39;s acquisition of YY live through this theory, with Baidu as the main body, focusing on the theoretical knowledge of merger and acquisition and strategic management. Through this case, to explore how to match resources between the current Internet industry to achieve their own benefits, how to acquire, how to deal with the sudden problems in the acquisition, and how to prevail on the mobile terminal, to find new revenue growth points through diversified strategies, and create a new mobile industry ecology. It is hoped that through the introduction of this case, it can help students to have a deeper understanding of the existing network ecology, digital economy, enterprise merger and acquisition, and strategic choices.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《收购兼并与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业并购、多元化战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
